     *
     * <pre>
     *                 +--------------+
     *         +&lt;----- | Created (0)  |
     *         |       +-----+--------+
     *         |             |
     *         |             v
     *         |       +----+--+------+
     *         |       | Re-          |
     *         +&lt;----- | Balancing (1)| --------&gt;+
     *         |       +-----+-+------+          |
     *         |             | ^                 |
     *         |             v |                 |
     *         |       +--------------+          v
     *         |       | Running (2)  | --------&gt;+
     *         |       +------+-------+          |
     *         |              |                  |
     *         |              v                  |
     *         |       +------+-------+     +----+-------+
     *         +-----&gt; | Pending      |     | Pending    |
